varargs string format_as_columns(string* items, int width, string indent,
   int order)

Format strings in "items" into columns. Other arguments are optional.
"width" determines the maximum screen width, "indent" is a string to
prepend to all new lines, if "order" is 1 then successive items fill rows first
if order is 0 (or not passed) then the more natural column first order is used.
left to right


